title: [Whistler's Pass, Road]
description: A cobblestone road begins here as a great circle.  The road heads to the northeast as it climbs up a large hill.  Fireflies flicker through the darkness around the road.
A cobblestone road begins here as a great circle.  The road heads to the northeast as it climbs up a large hill.  Dragonflies flit throughout the area.

A cobblestone road begins here as a great circle.  The road heads to the northeast as it climbs up a large hill past a tall slender stone tower.  Fireflies flicker through the darkness around the road.
